{"tid":1421671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(求文宣)誰大誰惡誰正確？","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T21:00:17.000Z","uid":296350,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"09bf983d3271522f2f1407d74ec54449f8be797a","tid":1421671,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">前線</span></span>開始不斷俾人話打普通市民， 畀人撩兩句就打人，政見唔同就打人， 破壞市民私人財產例如車<br />\n<br />\n（文宣）可唔可以幫手帶返個思維比淺王和你非甚至淺藍， 將源頭推返俾政府同黑警，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">幫前線解圍</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 冇一次係前線主動出手打市民， 只係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">自衛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 如果警方有公正執法，前線只需制服 ，交警方處理<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「現實係」</span></span> 前線制服個犯 ，交警方處理，警方放咗犯，拉前線，告前線！！<br />\n<br />\n3. 前線嘅冤屈，憤怒，可以點樣 彌補？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">公義何在？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發洩怒火冇辦法要全世界認同。<br />\n<br />\n如果你個女畀人強姦，你制服個犯 ，交畀警察，警察放咗佢，告你襲擊， <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你會點對個犯？你真係可以冷靜？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你個仔畀黑社會劈死咗，你制服個犯 ，交畀警察，警察放咗佢，告你襲擊， <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你會點對個犯？ 你真係可以冷靜？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一切<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">源頭</span></span>來自警方冇公平公正執法！！<br />\n當社會失去公義，我哋仲有咩辦法！！<br />\n<br />\nPS. 前線手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔可以主動出手</span></span>，一定要有片為證， 畀文宣做嘢，畀民間記者會發佈真相！！"},{"pid":"71b7ad9522a6cf38d4bc70a8d0bb6d6f76c7dc61","tid":1421671,"uid":156564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:40:49.000Z","msg":"唔好用藍字 睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"131876625cb61bb3bb7dae239442020201454f97","tid":1421671,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b